videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews tries cutting down the lane for a layup but is rejected by Purdue's Isaac Haas.
videos.headline: Haas swats Matthews

videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews takes it to the paint and fakes the layup attempt, leaving Purdue's Isaac Haas in the air and all over Matthews for the hard foul.
videos.headline: Matthews fakes out Haas with lethal pump fake

videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews finds Jon Teske cutting to the rim for the alley-oop layup.
videos.headline: Matthews finds Teske on the alley-oop finish

videos.description: Purdue's Carsen Edwards finds Isaac Haas cutting down the paint for a layup and the foul, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Haas converts and-1 layup

videos.description: Purdue's Carsen Edwards sets up Vincent Edwards on a dime for a two-handed dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Carsen sets up Vincent for two-handed slam

videos.description: Purdue's Dakota Mathias finds Carsen Edwards in transition for a 3-pointer in the first half vs. Michigan.
videos.headline: Edwards drains transition 3

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson fakes a pass to the corner and knocks down a 3-point shot.
videos.headline: Simpson buries open 3-pointer

videos.description: Purdue's P.J. Thompson finds Dakota Mathias open behind the arc for a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Thompson sets up Mathias for open 3

videos.description: Michigan's Charles Matthews connects with Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman for the corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman sinks corner 3

videos.description: Purdue's Vincent Edwards finds an opening behind the arc and converts from downtown, tying the game up at 68-68.
videos.headline: Edwards knocks down 3 to even game

videos.description: Purdue's Vincent Edwards dishes to Isaac Haas in the post for a tough layup and the foul, earning a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Haas converts post lay-in for and-1 chance

videos.description: Michigan's Moritz Wagner drives down the lane to sink a tough layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Wagner nails tough lay-in

videos.description: Purdue's Vincent Edwards finds Isaac Haas inside for the loud one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Haas throws down emphatic one-handed slam

videos.description: Michigan's Zavier Simpson swings the ball over to Muhammad-Ali Abdur-Rahkman for a contested 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Abdur-Rahkman drops career-high 26 points
